    {
      "id": "the-sundering",
      "title": "The Sundering",
      "type": "event",
      "world": "astrath-deeprealm",
      "visibility": "player",
      "canon": "canon",
      "aliases": [],
      "tags": [
        "cataclysm",
        "founding"
      ],
      "summary": "The cataclysm that split the old continent and ended the Third Age. The new calendar reckons years from the day the sky cracked.",
      "images": [],
      "body": "\nWhen the Twin Moons collided in the night sky, the firmament tore and the seas\nboiled. Half of the old continent slid beneath the waves; what remained\nbecame the Astrath Deeprealm. Survivors founded the great cities of\n[[Thornhold]] and [[Sunhaven]] in the years that followed.\n\nThis event marks year **0** of the *After Sundering* calendar.\n",
      "bodyHtml": "<p>When the Twin Moons collided in the night sky, the firmament tore and the seas\nboiled. Half of the old continent slid beneath the waves; what remained\nbecame the Astrath Deeprealm. Survivors founded the great cities of\n<a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"thornhold\" href=\"#/entity/thornhold\">Thornhold</a> and <a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"sunhaven\" href=\"#/entity/sunhaven\">Sunhaven</a> in the years that followed.</p>\n<p>This event marks year <strong>0</strong> of the <em>After Sundering</em> calendar.</p>\n",
      "frontmatter": {},
