    {
      "id": "the-old-keep",
      "title": "The Old Keep",
      "type": "ruin",
      "world": "astrath-deeprealm",
      "visibility": "rumor",
      "canon": "canon",
      "aliases": [],
      "tags": [
        "ruin",
        "mystery"
      ],
      "summary": "A crumbling fortress whispered of in taverns.",
      "images": [],
      "body": "\n# The Old Keep\n\nFew travelers have laid eyes on the keep and returned with a clear story.\nThose who have speak of [[A Lost King]] — though no record of such a ruler exists\nin the chronicles of [[Sunhaven]].\n",
      "bodyHtml": "<h1>The Old Keep</h1>\n<p>Few travelers have laid eyes on the keep and returned with a clear story.\nThose who have speak of <span class=\"atlas-unresolved\">A Lost King</span> — though no record of such a ruler exists\nin the chronicles of <a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"sunhaven\" href=\"#/entity/sunhaven\">Sunhaven</a>.</p>\n",
      "frontmatter": {},
      "sourcePath": "",
